data.description: Come see this beautiful, newly built farmhouse on three acres that includes a separate guest house and an unfinished partial basement. Built in 2017, this three bedroom, two-and-a-half bath home features a large master suite with separate his & hers walk-in closets, an additional powder room, open living and dining areas, generous mudroom with laundry and a convenient pet shower on the main level. Upstairs are two additional secondary bedrooms and full bath and downstairs is an additional +/- 700 unfinished square feet. The detached guest house is fully standalone from the main house with its own kitchen, washer and dryer hookups, one and a half bathrooms, living area, and upstairs bedroom. Your farmhouse dreams have been answered. Book your showing today!
